All title, ownership, and intellectual property rights in and to the Software —
including but not limited to the F-Man brand, the BSSS protocol, the Kingmaker
Sovereign Vault Protocol, the Ajo Settlement Layer, the YES CALL biometric gate,
and all associated trademarks, trade secrets, patents pending, and copyrights —
remain exclusively with PFF-TRUST.

This Licence does not convey any ownership interest in the Software to the
Licensee. Any feedback, suggestions, or improvement proposals submitted by the
Licensee become the sole property of PFF-TRUST without obligation of
compensation.

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
5. DATA PROTECTION & BIOMETRIC COMPLIANCE
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

  • The Licensee is the Data Controller for all customer data processed via
    the Software within the Licensee's platform.
  • PFF-TRUST acts as Data Processor and processes data only as instructed
    by the Licensee and in accordance with the NDPA 2023.
  • Biometric data is governed exclusively by the BSSS protocol: processed
    on-device, never transmitted, and represented externally only as a
    signed SUCCESS_TOKEN.
  • The Licensee must maintain a valid Data Protection Compliance Programme
    certified by NITDA.

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
