8. TERMINATION
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

This Licence is effective until terminated. The Licensor may terminate
immediately if the Licensee:

  (i)   Breaches any provision of this Licence and fails to cure within 14 days
  (ii)  Loses its CBN Agent Banking Licence or equivalent regulatory approval
  (iii) Becomes insolvent, enters administration, or ceases to trade
  (iv)  Is found to have stored raw biometric data in violation of the BSSS
  (v)   Fails to renew the annual Sovereign Licence Fee

Upon termination, the Licensee must immediately cease all use of the Software,
destroy all copies in its possession, and certify such destruction in writing
to PFF-TRUST within 7 business days.

